message.content:
cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.SI 

The paper deals with image annotation, which is a computer vision problem, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The use of metadata to generate neighborhoods of related images and the use of a deep neural network suggest that the paper could also belong to cs.IR (information retrieval) and cs.LG (machine learning). The experiments performed on the NUS-WIDE dataset suggest that the paper could also belong to cs.MM (multimedia) and cs.SI (social and information networks).
